summary: IoT Android Application for SAAS platform developed for Airport restrooms. Restroom cleaning staff gets alerts generated by system based on sensors located in restrooms
for cleaning required. Beacons scanning started in background for each cleaning alert assigned which are logged back to system to track cleaning task.


